{"tid":1556394,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【推俾更多人知】遠離共媒01，以保闔家平安","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T02:58:41.000Z","uid":295532,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8f108db0725b6077afbff205a6e16f7bb08f75","tid":1556394,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"我係P牌，希望大家可以幫手推呢個po俾更多人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信好多人都知輿論戰喺呢幾個月好緊要，堅定立場既人係唔會俾小小既輿論影響，揸緊個信念係幾緊要；但對於中間淺色呢啲游離份子黎講，就會有潛移默化既影響。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個po想同大家講講<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港01</span></strong>呢間打住「<strong>娼</strong>議型媒體」既<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅媒</strong></span>。相信好多人都對呢間野印象麻麻，會選擇unlinke、unfollow、block、no show佢。最近都有巴絲出po講過呢間野，其實呢間野好識玩網上輿論，開過好多專頁，平時扮中立，但關鍵時刻就會賣港，有好多page都係岩岩揾揾先知係佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲專頁定位報導同生活有關既事去拉近你同佢既距離，感覺上好像冇咩野，但既然係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>01</strong></span>出品，我覺得佢總有作用喺度。出面抗爭緊，入面風花雪月既情況成日發生，唔信既，睇下前晚港姐，有幾多人推波助瀾（唔係指lihkg）。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小fb既演算法，你like得多某啲專頁，fb就會不停feed相近既po俾你，等你發現時，未必太早。同樣，你like得、share得佢地，就等同一種鼓勵；就等於你一面鬧狗鐵，一面搭狗鐵一樣。見好多淺黃既人會share呢啲po，我覺得係件好危險既事，佢地係最快割蓆，光環上頭既人，而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>01</strong></span>喺關鍵事刻出聲會好影響到呢班人的主意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩喺fb揾就揾到一堆佢開既專頁，希望大家識做會unlike佢地。<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港01，61萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk01wemedia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk01wemedia%2F&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e61d726a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk01wemedia/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 01新聞，30萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk01.news/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk01.news%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=dfdcbdab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk01.news/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 隱形香港，18萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkrealism/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkrealism%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=d4d23dd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkrealism/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 01生活，20萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk01.life/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk01.life%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=7f4a8946\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk01.life/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 毛孩子：我們的故事，9.5萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk01.anistoryhk/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk01.anistoryhk%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=bdfc1faa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk01.anistoryhk/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 01娛樂，10萬人like<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk01.entertainment/?ref=br_rs[url][/url][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk01.entertainment%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs%5Burl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=1fdefe64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk01.entertainment/?ref=br_rs[url][/url][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n7. 01女生，10萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/beingms/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=h