k?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMartialabhk%2F&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=9a8d8952\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Martialabhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n20. 揾食姐，6萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/misseatsomuch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmisseatsomuch%2F&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e7e19668\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/misseatsomuch/</a><br />\n<br />\n21. e肚仔，2799人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/eatojoy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Featojoy%2F&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=5ec8d318\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/eatojoy/</a><br />\n<br />\n22. 一物 object a，7.2萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/objectahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fobjectahk%2F&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=98c74f16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/objectahk/</a><br />\n<br />\n23. 形而，2.4萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/metahk01/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmetahk01%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=68db858e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/metahk01/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n<br />\n24. 扭耳仔 New Ears Music，3.9萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/newearsmusichk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnewearsmusichk%2F&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e5ba00ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/newearsmusichk/</a><br />\n<br />\n25. 第二身，5.3萬人like<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2ndskinT2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2ndskinT2%2F&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=ed6aa7cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2ndskinT2/</a><br />\n<br />\n下面呢個係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>01</strong></span>官網既分頁，可以跟住呢個網既分欄揾晒佢既專頁出黎，有啲分頁歸返大專頁度的。暫時揾到呢啲，但相信過一段時間，佢又會開新一啲page去呃下人：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AW3R0OG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAW3R0OG.jpg&h=f414967d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能會有人認為咁做好不智，咁樣會令自己miss左唔同方面既資訊。但問心，呢啲page unlike晒其實對我影響唔太多；反而，如果你覺得影響大，咁你就要反思下點解會咁。<br />\n<br />\n又有人認為多一個渠道聽多個意見唔係更好咩？但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>共媒01</strong></span>適時賣港，喺某啲關鍵位，例如勇武升級與否，可能<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>01</strong></span>評論既某幾個字打入你既諗法，就會令你轉軚。Inception有句講得好好：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;What is the most resilient parasite? Bacteria? A virus? An intestinal worm? An idea.<br />\nResilient, highly contagious. Once an idea has taken hold of the brain it&rsquo;s almost impossible to eradicate. An idea that is fully formed &ndash; fully understood &ndash; that sticks; right in there somewhere.&rdquo; - Dom Cobb, Inception<br />\n<br />\n唔好太高估自己堅定既立場，喺一啲位你企唔穩立場，搖擺不定，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>01</strong></span>呢啲媒體就發揮作用啦，咁就出事了。「永不割蓆」好多時都係人講你講，拾人牙慧既野你會做，我都會做，而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>01</strong></span>，更想你拾佢牙慧。<br />\n<br />\nFor TLDR人：<br />\nUnlike所有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港01</strong></span>既專頁，馬上、即刻、唔好諗！<br />\nUnlike所有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港01</strong></span>既專頁，馬上、即刻、唔好諗！<br />\nUnlike所有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港01</strong></span>既專頁，馬上、即刻、唔好諗！"},{"pid":"7232ba069399126a13f04ce1fe662a1fd605b01a","tid":1556394,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n快d unfollow <br />\n否則關鍵時刻會被紅底01斬到一頸血<br />\n<br />\n<code>831黑警恐襲 721元朗恐怖襲擊 811黑警還眼     #星火： 98190979 #民陣: 65499452 我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要去醫院驗傷  我唔會解鎖電話 我唔會簽任何文件</code>"},{"pid":"2b02796d4b0f0630da5096831b1aac596ed44d2d","tid":1556394,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"